data.description: Ever want a home that feels tucked away into a forest? This home is for you! This 3/2 split bedroom floor plan has an open concept center for the family to gather around an amazing fireplace. Leave the back doors open and extend that area out to the enormous screened patio making the outdoors part of your living space! Besides those things, this lovely home has a new tankless water heater (2023), brand new carpet in bedrooms (2023), all the large windows have been replaced with hurricane proof ones (2022), and the GORGEOUS hardwoods throughout the main are all such bonuses! And you have a huge yard to enjoy where there has already been a beautiful garden started for you to continue growing your own amazing flowers and veggies. Come see this one soon!
